data.description: Rare 2.99% Interest Rate Option Available - this home currently has a 2.99% interest rate assumable mortgage, contact an agent ASAP!! Walk through this home with just a click https://my.matterport.com/show/?m=S7HaH6r1iDc Seller is motivated and did a GREAT price Improvement to catch your eye! Remodeled 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom home in a popular Central Florida community called Dukes Lake. If you need space, here is your place! The formal Dining & Living room are bonus areas that could be turned into another bedroom or office if needed. The large open concept with the Great Room/Kitchen/dinette is perfect for gatherings. Don't believe me? Check out this video walk through to see for yourself https://vimeo.com/826536680?share=copy  You will love having the 2 sinks and 2 pantries in the kitchen, so much cabinet & counter space too. The Master Suite has 2 walk in closets, a spacious bathroom with shower, soaking tub & water closet. The 3 extra bedrooms are split from master so everyone can have their own quiet space. Almost all of the interior has NEW flooring & NEW paint. Roof 2017, HVAC 2022 & 2017. You have the luxury of being out of the hustle & bustle of a big busy city but you are close to all necessities, the City of Groveland has events like the Farmer's Market, live entertainment, food trucks etc. Getting to Orlando is a breeze with the Turnpike just 9 miles away, The Villages, Walt Disney World®, other theme parks & MCO Orlando International Airport just 45mins or less away. Drive a little further and stick your toes in the sand of Florida's World Famous Beaches. What are you waiting for? Book your private tour today.
